#: 21337012-0-335
msgctxt "21337012-0-335"
msgid ""
"Guardian Sud-Hareem, Expedition Leader\n"
"Praxin Douare, Expedition Lieutenant\n"
"\n"
"Guardian Sud-Hareem, aided by Praxin Douare, will lead a small expedition of "
"Fighters Guild mercenaries to investigate the caves designated as "
"Spindleclutch. Rumors have circulated that abnormally large spiders infest "
"the caves. Should the creatures prove threatening, the expedition is hereby "
